  "prompt": "Who is the best broadband service provider in Mysore?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" broadband service provider can be subjective and depends on various factors such as speed, reliability, customer service, coverage, and pricing. However, some of the popular broadband service providers in Mysore include:\n\n1. **BSNL (Bharat Sanchar Nigam Limited)**: BSNL is a government-owned company that provides extensive coverage and various plans at competitive prices.\n\n2. **ACT Fibernet**: Known for high-speed internet and reliable service. ACT Fibernet is popular in urban areas for its fiber-optic broadband services.\n\n3. **Airtel Xstream Fiber**: Airtel offers high-speed internet with a range of plans and additional benefits like bundled subscriptions to streaming services.\n\n4. **JioFiber**: Reliance Jio's broadband service offers competitive pricing, high-speed internet, and various bundled services.\n\n5. **Hathway Broadband**: Hathway is another known provider offering various plans and generally reliable service.\n\nTo determine the best provider for your needs, consider factors like specific plans available, customer reviews in your area, the quality of customer service, and any additional benefits they may offer. You may also want to check for the latest reviews and ratings from local users to make an informed decision.",
